      "content": "that's a great start. i want to make the counter-arguments look even weaker so the paper is more convincing. like, how should i frame the 'meritocracy' argument? i want to show why people who use it to defend the status quo are basically just ignoring how the system actually works. can you help me write a paragraph that addresses that?",
